      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HOOKED ON GIN (7) was safely held last time out, finishing sixth at this track over 390m behind TOPPER SNOWDRIFT (23.16) in a Grade 5. Better than the latest effort and deserves another chance. THERMAL FLAME (1) had a tough draw to overcome and was game in defeat when only half a length from Distorted Humour in third (17.27) at Healesville. Expected to be in this for a long way. TOPPER SNOWDRIFT (8) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by half a length at this track in a handy 22.73 beating We Are South. One of the prime contenders. SUGAR SHINE (2) can measure up with the right run.",
